      <title>国库在柔和的二月劳动力市场数据后延长了收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/treasuries-extend-gains-after-soft-february-labor-market-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在每月的就业报告显示出弱点的迹象之后，美国国债增加了，增加了2025年的收益，这使得交易者对今年晚些时候削减联邦储备金利率的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/treasuries-extend-gains-after-soft-february-labor-market-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 14:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗在2022年脂肪手指闪光崩溃上被瑞士交换调节器罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/citi-fined-by-swiss-exchange-regulator-over-2022-fat-finger-flash-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团（Citigroup Inc.）在伦敦员工的脂肪手指贸易造成了2022年欧洲股票的爆发事故后，被瑞士证券交易所监管机构罚款500,000瑞士法郎（568,000美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/citi-fined-by-swiss-exchange-regulator-over-2022-fat-finger-flash-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 14:09:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普贸易战争，制裁抓地力已经紧密的重油市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-trade-wars-sanctions-grip-already-tight-heavy-oil-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战争和制裁正在收紧繁重的原油市场，提高了石油的价格，并为美国最大的炼油中心筹集了成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-trade-wars-sanctions-grip-already-tight-heavy-oil-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在2月增加了151,000个工作岗位，失业率为4.1％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-07/us-adds-151-000-jobs-in-february-unemployment-rate-4-1-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2月，美国非农业工资率增加了151,000，而失业率出乎意料地提高了4.1％。迈克尔·麦基（Michael McKee）分解了彭博电视台（Bloomberg Television）上的数字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-07/us-adds-151-000-jobs-in-february-unemployment-rate-4-1-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:56:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Kazaks说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/ecb-needs-open-mind-on-april-cut-due-to-uncertainty-kazaks-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据管理理事会成员马丁斯·卡扎克斯（Martins Kazaks）称，欧洲中央银行应保留所有选择，以便下个月的利率决定，因为经济前景取决于难以预测的地缘政治冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/ecb-needs-open-mind-on-april-cut-due-to-uncertainty-kazaks-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:47:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过数月的强劲增长，加拿大的就业市场摊位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/canada-s-job-market-stalls-after-months-of-strong-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过数月的稳定增长，加拿大的就业市场意外喘口气，但由于更少的人在寻找工作，失业率保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/canada-s-job-market-stalls-after-months-of-strong-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国能源总监将寻求200亿美元以补充石油储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-energy-chief-plans-to-seek-20-billion-to-refill-oil-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国能源部长克里斯·赖特（Chris Wright）计划寻求高达200亿美元，以实现唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的目标，即将全国耗尽的石油储备金以最大能力加油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/us-energy-chief-plans-to-seek-20-billion-to-refill-oil-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 12:51:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股票退缩，关税不适，豪华不适</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/european-stocks-drop-as-tariff-jitters-trigger-broad-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股票在周五撤退，因为迅速不断发展的关税背景和对利率的不确定性促使投资者锁定利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/european-stocks-drop-as-tariff-jitters-trigger-broad-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 08:17:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税骚动统治时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油上涨周五，但由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的竞争，不受重大贸易伙伴的关税，对全球市场注入波动和不确定性，这是自去年下半年以来每周最大下降的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 23:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
